# Multi-line call args: RelPos is honoured end-to-end. A Newline
# RelPos on an arg puts it on its own line; a NewSection RelPos on
# the closing ')' (blank line before ')' in the source) is preserved
# as a blank line in the output. RelPos is data the user put there
# and the formatter must not silently delete it.
-- in.cue --
x: strings.Join(
			a,
	            ",",

	)
-- out/relpos --
x: strings.Join(
	a,
	",",

)
-- out/norelpos --
x: strings.Join(a, ",")
